  m_text: '<align=center><b>Welcome Commander!</b></align>


    Game includes optional
    web3 elements that require you to use and interact with 3rd party apps such as
    crypto wallets, dex platforms and nft marketplaces. All these features are here
    to enhance your gameplay but are completely optional and don''t impact core gameplay.


    Our
    goal is to build the game for the players - together with the players. If you
    wish to take more active role please reach out on our socials.


    Game is
    under active development and might contain bugs, errors and missing features
    that can impact your experience. During the development period we might occasionally
    delete the user accounts and data.'
